</hgroup>

<article> 
    <h5>Problem</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>How does the server indicate that a featrue is not supported?</li>
        <li>Client and Server evolve at differnet rates.</li>  
        <li>Multiple server implemenations which may or may not implement the same features as the client.</li>  
    </ul>  
</article>

