<article> 
    <h5>Solution</h5> 
    <ul>
        <li>Use Resource Description mechnisim:
<pre>{ 
    "resources" : { 
        "streamingQuotes" : "/Stream_Quote...",
        "tickQuotes" : "/Tick_Quotes...",
        "currencies" : "/Currenies...",
        ...
    }
}</pre>    
            vs. 
<pre>{ 
    "resources" : {  
        "tickQuotes" : "/Tick_Quotes...",
        "currencies" : "/Currenies...",
        ...
    }
}</pre>
            This Resource Description doesn't support viewing Streaming Quotes.
        </li>
    </ul>
</article> 

<article> 
    <h5>Example</h5> 
    <ul>
        <li>Glimpse Resource Description:
<pre>{
    "version": "1.0",
    "resources" : { 
        "glimpse_request" : "Request?requestId={requestId}&version={version}{&Callback}",
        "glimpse_ajax" : "Ajax?parentRequestId={parentRequestId}&version={version}{&Callback}",
        "glimpse_history" : "History?version={version}{&top}{&Callback}",
        ...
    },
    ...
}</pre>
            vs.
<pre>{
    "version": "1.0",
    "resources" : { 
        "glimpse_request" : "Request?requestId={requestId}&version={version}{&Callback}", 
        "glimpse_history" : "History?version={version}{&top}{&Callback}",
        ...
    },
    ...
}</pre>
            This Resource Description doesn't support viewing Ajax Requests.
        </li>
    </ul>
</article>
 

